OL,3,C'I want to change the law before my
OL,4,Cwife dies': Bereaved dad campaigns for
OL,5,Cson
OL,7,FJohnny Santer has been working to
OL,8,Fintroduce 'Gabe's Law' to make safety
OL,9,Fbarriers taller and prevent future
OL,10,Fdeaths. He spoke to our political
OL,11,Fcorrespondent, Lise McNally.
OL,13,FA father who is fighting to make multi-
OL,14,Fstorey car parks safer after his son
OL,15,Ffell to his death says he hopes to
OL,16,Fchange the law before his wife's
OL,17,Fterminal cancer progresses.
OL,19,FGabriel Santer was 15-years-old when
OL,20,Fhe fell from the top of a multi-storey
OL,21,Fcar park in October 2020.
