OL,3,C'I want to change the law before my
OL,4,Cwife dies': Bereaved dad campaigns for
OL,5,Cson
OL,7,FHe had been with friends at the Q-car
OL,8,Fpark, in Liverpool city centre, and
OL,9,Fhad just texted his mum to tell her
OL,10,Fwhat he wanted for tea, but never came
OL,11,Fhome.
OL,13,FSince then, his dad Johnny Santer has
OL,14,Fcampaigned to increase the minimum
OL,15,Fheight of barriers on top of car parks
OL,16,Fthrough the Multi-Storey Car Parks
OL,17,F(Safety) Bill, known as Gabe's Law.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
