OL,3,C'I want to change the law before my
OL,4,Cwife dies': Bereaved dad campaigns for
OL,5,Cson
OL,7,FBut he says "time is of the essence"
OL,8,Ffor his wife and Gabriel's mother to
OL,9,Fsee the law passed before her cancer,
OL,10,Fwhich she has been living with for the
OL,11,Flast 10 years, progresses any further.
OL,13,FJohnny said: "It would be lovely for
OL,14,Fher knowing Gabe's law has been
OL,15,Fenacted to protect the most vulnerable
OL,16,Fpeople in our communities and make
OL,17,Fsure no other family goes through the
OL,18,Fpain we have."
