OL,3,C'I want to change the law before my
OL,4,Cwife dies': Bereaved dad campaigns for
OL,5,Cson
OL,7,FOn Monday, 7 July, Johnny met with the
OL,8,FBuilding Safety Minister Alex Norris
OL,9,Fto make his case. If the law were to
OL,10,Fpass, it would see:
OL,12,F"When you look as I have done
OL,13,Fextensively into this problem,
OL,14,Fspecifically surrounding multi-story
OL,15,Fcar parks, you realise we've got a
OL,16,Freally big problem", Johnny said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
