OL,3,C'I want to change the law before my
OL,4,Cwife dies': Bereaved dad campaigns for
OL,5,Cson
OL,7,F"We are having repeated preventable
OL,8,Fdeaths - six at the last count in
OL,9,FLiverpool alone since Gabriel's death,
OL,10,Fand unbelievably another from the same
OL,11,Foperator as the one that Gabriel fell
OL,12,Ffrom. It has to stop."
OL,14,FThe company that runs the site where
OL,15,FGabe died have previously said that
OL,16,Ftheir car park outperformed the
OL,17,Frequired building regulations and they
OL,18,Fwere cleared of any wrongdoing.
