OL,3,C'I want to change the law before my
OL,4,Cwife dies': Bereaved dad campaigns for
OL,5,Cson
OL,7,FBut the Liverpool Garston MP Maria
OL,8,FEagle believes that is exactly why the
OL,9,Fregulations need to change, and says
OL,10,Fthe best way of preventing future
OL,11,Fdeaths is to "stop it being so easy."
OL,13,FShe said: "At the moment the law
OL,14,Frequires only a very low barrier, that
OL,15,Fpeople can easily topple, fall or jump
OL,16,Fover. So, make the barrier higher,
OL,17,Fpeople can't fall, and they can't
OL,18,Fjump, its simple as that."
