OL,3,C'I want to change the law before my
OL,4,Cwife dies': Bereaved dad campaigns for
OL,5,Cson
OL,7,FAt the beginning of July, the Prime
OL,8,FMinister Sir Keir Starmer promised to
OL,9,Freview safety standards in multi-
OL,10,Fstories to "prevent future tragedies."
OL,12,FSpeaking in Parliament on 2 July, he
OL,13,Fsaid the Government will conduct a
OL,14,Fcall for evidence on minimum barrier
OL,15,Fheights in car parks.
