OL,7,FHe added: "We will conduct a call for
OL,8,Fevidence on part K of the building
OL,9,Fregulations about minimum guarding
OL,10,Fheights, so that necessary protections
OL,11,Fare in place to prevent future
OL,12,Ftragedies.
OL,14,F"We will also look at the contents of
OL,15,Fthe Bill."
